query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as cnt, SUM(ownerAmount) as total_revenue, MIN(DATE_FORMAT(startDate, '%Y-%m-%d')) as earliest, MAX(DATE_FORMAT(startDate, '%Y-%m-%d')) as latest
FROM bookings 
WHERE status = 'confirmed' 
AND startDate >= '2025-07-01' 
AND startDate <= CURDATE();
